%Disease Diet

% Covid-19

covid_diet:-
        write('Suggested Diet for Covid-19: '),nl,
        write('1. Increase your intake of Vitamin C and Zinc.'),nl,
        write('2. Eat foods that are high in antioxidants like berries, dark leafy greens, and fatty fish.'),nl,
        write('3. Eat foods rich in monounsaturated fatty acids, such as olive oil, nuts, and avocados.'),nl,
        write('4. Increase your intake of prebiotics, such as garlic, onions, and asparagus.'),nl,
        write('5. Eat probiotic-rich foods, such as yogurt, kefir, and sauerkraut.').
